        <updateDate>2021-03-03T21:19:14Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Academic Partnerships Lead Us to Success Act or the A PLUS Act</strong>&nbsp; </p> <p>This bill creates a framework under which states may receive federal elementary and secondary education funds on a consolidated basis and use such funds for any educational purpose permitted by state law. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
